        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1955-09-08T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1955-09-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="173"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d173">
                <head>173. Telegram 696 to Geneva<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d173fn1">Source:
                        Department of State, Central Files, 611.93/9–455. Confidential; Priority.
                        Drafted by Osborn.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1955-09-08">September 8, 1955, 6:01 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d173-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d173-1"/>
                <p>696. For <persName corresp="#p_JUA_1">Johnson</persName>. Department’s 678.</p>
                <p>Immigration Naturalization Service reports 90 Chinese left Honolulu for Far East
                    between July 11 August 31 inclusive. Total departures given next to last
                    paragraph should be changed to 173.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_HH_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Hoover</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
